{"tid":1220663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢作為最前線嘅一員 我真心想同所有有心人道歉","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:57:51.000Z","uid":30205,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f0922dc397ba106ea1dd97549062ccf0c325f78f","tid":1220663,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:58:36.000Z","msg":"前日發夢自己企喺最前線 同被人顏射嗰位兄弟差唔多位置 亦一直留到最後半夜撒離<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日keep住發夢去整理思緒 甚至同朋友討論點可以守得好啲<br />\n直至呢兩日慢慢睇返新聞同片段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5ys4jZ-cQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ5ys4jZ-cQY&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=23dabba4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5ys4jZ-cQY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lSsIy9o2CQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlSsIy9o2CQs&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=2a41b3ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lSsIy9o2CQs</a><br />\n<br />\n聽到呢兩段我真係喊到收唔到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地前線可以守得更加好 哪怕拖多幾分鐘 可能都保護到後面嘅一班中學生同小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我想講 前線嘅義士 首先諗嘅從來唔係去衝擊班狗 當然達到守住陣線 成功圍堵就最理想<br />\n但我地最大嘅理念 係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">萬一班狗同速龍衝出來發癲 都要保護到後面嘅朋友</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你地有任何受傷 我想講聲<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對唔住</span></span> 我地守唔住 唔夠時間畀大家撒離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880ea76aeaa0fdd415e751d47d6cde4e7024da30","tid":1220663,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1718cdb23e714721966d4b8bc180f705a33095","tid":1